info.description: # OpenTelemetry Semantic Conventions extensions for gen-AI applications This is an extension of the standard [OpenTelemetry Semantic Conventions](https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions) for gen AI applications. It defines additional attributes for spans that are useful for debugging and monitoring prompts, completions, token usage, etc.
info.name: opentelemetry-semantic-conventions-ai
info.summary: OpenTelemetry Semantic Conventions Extension for Large Language Models
